            Individuals do not need to sign up for access to our job and event board. We do not own the information on the board.<br><br>

            <h5><i class="icon-location"></i> Contact</h5>
                
            For complaints regarding the mailing system, please contact: <br>
            Alan Yuan<br>
            alan.yuan@mail.utoronto.ca<br><br>

        </div>
    </div>
             
</div>